Hey, I'm Fishbrain.

Well done for making it in!

Why don't you get yourself a nice brew to sooth your mind?

# SOLSMASHER

The debut track by **CTRL**.

When Dede, Gatt, Fishbrain, and BSK met on the block, like four comets from the four corners of the Earth, they made a STAMP on the chain that would ripple throughout history. This fist shaped stamp is referred by archaologists as the SolSmasher.

When Fiery fist smashed into the Earth, comet catchers excavated the fist shaped imprint and used it as a STAMP for 404 talismans. It is said, talismans hold the power of the energy held by the 4 individuals at the beginning of the great Unfolding.

# ASYNC PLAYER (wip)

This is a work in progress for an interactive Async piece.

# THE CONCEPT

Each LAYER will contain the 3 stems to choose from for that layer. Holders of Async pieces are able to live mix between the stems so they can hear each version of the mix. This is built to be part of a private experience only accessible by holders of the piece, or as an interactive demo for Async.
